    {
      "sentence_id": 176,
      "text": "Her crew, of which only eigh- \nteen survived out of about an hundred, had added \nto the natural ferocity of their temper, by a free \nuse of opium, combined with the juice of a root, call- \n\n\n\n19 \n\ned hang; these stimulants, when associated with their \nMahometan persuasion of the doctrine of predesti- \nnation, render them totally exempt from fear, pro- \ndace the most ungovernable rage and desperation, and \nstimulate them to deeds of the most savage and dia- \nbolical barbarity.",
